00:29:06,432 --> 00:29:11,089
♫  I cheer for you  ♫

414
00:29:11,089 --> 00:29:15,164
♫  We can fly  ♫

415
00:29:15,164 --> 00:29:18,300
♫  There are unlimited expectations  ♫

416
00:29:18,300 --> 00:29:19,870
Cherry?

417
00:29:21,120 --> 00:29:22,900
Cherry...

418
00:29:25,080 --> 00:29:27,680
- What's wrong? 
 - Jiang Qiao Xi...

419
00:29:28,320 --> 00:29:30,019
What about Jiang Qiao Xi?

420
00:29:30,019 --> 00:29:33,659
Jiang Qiao Xi met my former Olympiad teammates 
 at the training school

421
00:29:33,659 --> 00:29:35,620
and got my cellphone number from them.

422
00:29:35,620 --> 00:29:36,739
And then?

423
00:29:36,739 --> 00:29:40,380
He called me and asked for your number.

424
00:29:40,380 --> 00:29:42,000
Get to the point.

425
00:29:42,000 --> 00:29:44,860
He's calling you right now!

426
00:29:44,860 --> 00:29:47,000
You're not answering!

427
00:30:01,239 --> 00:30:06,959
 The number you dialed is busy. Try again later. 

428
00:30:18,559 --> 00:30:22,640
One, two, three, four...

429
00:30:22,640 --> 00:30:24,450
Jiang Qiao Xi?

430
00:30:25,019 --> 00:30:27,680
Hello, Cherry.

431
00:30:28,360 --> 00:30:30,199
Jiang Qiao Xi.

432
00:30:30,199 --> 00:30:32,199
How have you been lately?

433
00:30:37,399 --> 00:30:38,999
I...

434
00:30:40,280 --> 00:30:44,339
Did something happen?

435
00:30:44,339 --> 00:30:46,610
I'm fine.

436
00:30:46,610 --> 00:30:48,540
I've been doing well lately.

437
00:30:49,120 --> 00:30:53,499
The only bad part is that you're not here.

438
00:30:54,219 --> 00:30:57,080
But you'll come back to school eventually,

439
00:30:57,080 --> 00:31:00,900
so it's not that bad.

440
00:31:02,979 --> 00:31:04,560
Don't worry about me.

441
00:31:04,560 --> 00:31:08,680
As for school, as long as I'm not challenged,

442
00:31:08,680 --> 00:31:11,380
nothing can beat Lin Cherry.

443
00:31:15,540 --> 00:31:18,779
So... How are things over there?

444
00:31:21,780 --> 00:31:25,219
As long as you're okay, I'm fine.

445
00:31:27,680 --> 00:31:30,399
 Jiang Qiao Xi, it's lights out soon. 

446
00:31:31,540 --> 00:31:36,499
Are you not allowed to talk on the phone for long?

447
00:31:36,499 --> 00:31:39,120
No, but it's lights out soon.

448
00:31:39,120 --> 00:31:41,559
It's okay, we can talk a bit more.

449
00:31:43,079 --> 00:31:45,616
About what?

450
00:31:47,424 --> 00:31:51,210
You... you should go to bed early.

451
00:31:51,210 --> 00:31:54,060
Getting enough rest is important.

452
00:31:54,060 --> 00:31:59,640
I hope we will do well when we meet again.

453
00:32:00,859 --> 00:32:02,459
We will!

454
00:32:26,759 --> 00:32:30,360
Good! Nice!

455
00:32:30,360 --> 00:32:33,190
Lots of athletic grace!

456
00:32:33,190 --> 00:32:35,420
Excellent sense of rhythm!

457
00:32:35,424 --> 00:32:37,519
♫  What am I singing?  ♫

458
00:32:37,519 --> 00:32:40,408
Very good, Lin Qi Le. Significant improvement.

459
00:32:40,408 --> 00:32:42,900
♫  In the end, you're my theme song  ♫

460
00:32:42,900 --> 00:32:44,746
♫  What are you saying?  ♫

461
00:32:44,746 --> 00:32:48,576
♫  I'll remember even after hearing it once  ♫

462
00:32:48,576 --> 00:32:50,420
♫  Hear it twice and it burns  ♫

463
00:32:50,420 --> 00:32:52,173
♫  What am I doing?  ♫

464
00:32:52,173 --> 00:32:53,500
♫  Everything feels like  ♫

465
00:32:53,500 --> 00:32:54,740
- Xiao Man. 
 - Xiao Man.

466
00:32:54,740 --> 00:32:57,300
- Are you okay? 
 - Should we go to the infirmary?

467
00:32:58,140 --> 00:32:59,280
Let me catch my breath.

468
00:32:59,280 --> 00:33:00,980
Are you okay?

469
00:33:02,160 --> 00:33:05,580
It's okay, Coach. Lin Qi Le didn't mean it.

470
00:33:05,580 --> 00:33:09,060
No, you stepped on me earlier!

471
00:33:13,280 --> 00:33:15,819
Yes, yes, I stepped on you.

472
00:33:15,819 --> 00:33:17,920
I'm sorry, Classmate Lin Qi Le.

473
00:33:17,920 --> 00:33:20,519
What do you mean by "Yes, yes"?

474
00:33:20,519 --> 00:33:23,219
All right, enough. Everyone, take a break.

475
00:33:23,219 --> 00:33:25,919
You two, take her over there to rest.

476
00:33:27,459 --> 00:33:29,259
Be careful.

477
00:33:43,579 --> 00:33:46,220
 Xiao Man, are you all right? 

478
00:33:46,739 --> 00:33:51,360
 I'm fine. I hope this 
 won't affect my performance later. 

479
00:33:52,080 --> 00:33:54,019
 Lin Qi Le went too far. 

480
00:33:54,019 --> 00:33:58,060
Coach just praised her, 
 and she immediately hurt you.

481
00:33:58,060 --> 00:34:02,156
Is she trying to replace you as lead dancer?

482
00:34:02,740 --> 00:34:04,500
No.

483
00:34:05,380 --> 00:34:08,050
I don't even know 
 if I should stay here anymore.

484
00:34:09,439 --> 00:34:13,176
If anyone should leave, it's her. 
 People like her shouldn't stay.

485
00:34:13,176 --> 00:34:16,880
She has trained so hard. She won't leave.

486
00:34:18,099 --> 00:34:20,270
You're not quitting, are you?

487
00:34:20,270 --> 00:34:23,220
- If you leave, I'll leave too. 
 - Same here.

488
00:34:23,240 --> 00:34:25,340
I'm with you, Xiao Man.

489
00:34:25,979 --> 00:34:27,720
Is this what you said.

490
00:34:27,720 --> 00:34:30,940
 If you leave, others will replace you anyway. 

491
00:34:30,940 --> 00:34:34,059
If I can teach Lin Qi Le, I can also teach others.

492
00:34:34,059 --> 00:34:37,699
Perfect timing. I might even 
 volunteer to be the team captain.

493
00:34:38,920 --> 00:34:42,039
Cen Xiao Man, don't go back on your word.

494
00:35:06,380 --> 00:35:09,080
I know you're not mad at me anymore.

495
00:35:09,080 --> 00:35:12,170
I heard you standing up for me today.

496
00:35:16,999 --> 00:35:19,160
Stop pretending!

497
00:35:19,160 --> 00:35:22,470
You were so cool standing up for me today.

498
00:35:28,180 --> 00:35:31,160
Let's order our uniforms 
 at the uniform shop this Sunday.

499
00:35:31,160 --> 00:35:33,619
After that, let's go shopping.

500
00:35:33,619 --> 00:35:37,610
Didn't you say I've become unfashionable 
 since transferring to Experimental High School?

501
00:35:37,610 --> 00:35:41,480
You're the fashion expert. Give me some tips.

502
00:35:42,579 --> 00:35:45,119
Let's get milk tea after shopping.

503
00:35:45,119 --> 00:35:48,890
After drinking our milk tea, 
 we will officially seal our reconciliation.

504
00:35:48,890 --> 00:35:50,460
Deal?

505
00:35:51,660 --> 00:35:53,660
I'll think about it.

